<p>On Monday, Wright thanked the over 110K fans who donated a dollar to stream Sunday's virtual Princess Bride reunion benefitting the Democratic Party of Wisconsin.</p>

<p>'I truly thank all of you who showed up for the Princess Bride table read yesterday!' the House of Cards alum - who boasts 1.2M social media followers - gushed.</p>

<p>'What an incredible turnout. Let's keep staying involved and make this change together #vote.'</p>

<p>Comedian Patton Oswalt moderated the virtual event which drew orignial castmembers Cary Elwes, Chris Sarandon, Mandy Patinkin, Billy Crystal, Carol Kane, Wallace Shaw, and Christopher Guest.    </p>

